<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center; font-size: 125%; font-weight: bold; background:#ffff99;">Constrictor knot</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center;">
<div class="center">
<div class="floatnone"><a href="/wiki/File:Constrictors-Header.jpg" class="image" title="Constrictors-Header.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d8/Constrictors-Header.jpg/250px-Constrictors-Header.jpg" width="250" height="250" border="0" /></a></div>
