<th style="">Related</th>
<td class="" style=""><a href="/wiki/Clove_hitch" title="Clove hitch">Clove hitch</a>, <a href="/wiki/Transom_knot" title="Transom knot">Transom knot</a>, <a href="/wiki/Strangle_knot" title="Strangle knot">Strangle knot</a>, <a href="/wiki/Miller%27s_knot" title="Miller's knot">Miller's knot</a>, <a href="/wiki/Boa_knot" title="Boa knot">Boa knot</a></td>
